# ================================================================
# AI Data Analysis Assistant - Environment Variables Template
# ================================================================

# DeepSeek API Key (Required for LLM features)
# Get from: https://platform.deepseek.com/
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Backend URL (For frontend - update when deployed)
API_URL=http://localhost:7860

# ================================================================
# Usage Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env
# 2. Replace xxxxxxxxx with your actual API key
# 3. Never commit .env to git!
# ================================================================